// Domain-specific aggregators (ITER core, JET D-T 1997, NSTX, SPARC,
// solar corona, magnetosphere, Z-pinch operating points) live in
// `stdlib/<domain>/` adapters — NOT here. This kernel is the
// reusable, parity-tested primitive layer.
